id":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:01:18.000Z","msg":"話自己用開、聽開乜乜乜嚟做證據真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"acfcd8e7fc64882671f873fd5d89f5eb246a0703","tid":279201,"uid":99561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話自己用開、聽開乜乜乜嚟做證據真係得啖笑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留名等睇你比數據"},{"pid":"b7a87fd1170b7fc19a2ca183c841d97efafe3974","tid":279201,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:03:05.000Z","msg":"大陸都叫的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9419bbf1a5fef10a30969aa2cf2fdae40777a40d","tid":279201,"uid":5073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:04:20.000Z","msg":"我記憶中，打的呢句係我廣東省d親戚講先嘅。<br />\n我第一次聽到覺得超un耳，所以印象好深。<br />\n以前香港從來無打的呢個講法，至少90年代前仲未有。"},{"pid":"eec6a4956996119e79a20c01844f851aa9fa5a22","tid":279201,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:04:49.000Z","msg":"樓主幾多歲？<br />\n以前香港冇人講打的<br />\n係講搭的士，截的士<br />\n大陸人先會講打的"},{"pid":"ee85ecaab0a463cbbabd963b636af4cc9f5fe53f","tid":279201,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:07:46.000Z","msg":"截的士係人話<br />\n打的係蝗話"},{"pid":"09cfb7dab7bf0cd17e55bca2a0c11b2ae46b3849","tid":279201,"uid":67407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主幾多歲？<br />\n以前香港冇人講打的<br />\n係講搭的士，截的士<br />\n大陸人先會講打的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有無睇過我講咩架<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">的士係香港獨有語言</span></span><br />\n即係由Taxi譯翻做廣東話<br />\n大陸/台灣 叫計程車<br />\n<br />\n自己廿幾歲，印象中細細個已經聽過屋企人講（全部都係香港出世，唔好老屈我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"718665ce95a7f2f86c0082f409c0d0867f0787fb","tid":279201,"uid":26942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:09:25.000Z","msg":"以前香港人講塔的<br />\nd 大陸人當普通話聽落個塔字咪變成打"},{"pid":"05e7738bb722fbd